snippet.title: Let's Build a Zoo: Aquarium Odyssey Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
LET'S GET SPLASHING! We're super excited to announce Let's Build A Zoo: Aquarium Odyssey #DLC! A whole new campaign, 50+ new species, 7 new enclosures, 110+ new shops, decorations and other wonderful things! Keep your eyes peeled for the release date!

Wishlist Let's Build a Zoo: Aquarium Odyssey now on Steam!
https://bit.ly/Aquarium_Odyssey

Join the official Discord: http://discord.gg/letsbuildazoo

#LetsBuildAZoo | #IndieGames
